title: The Cigar Conspiracy
itunes:title: The Cigar Conspiracy
description:
With the cigar industry in consolidation mode, is there some one or group behind it. We think there can be, and we discuss The Cigar Conspiracy. Also, joining us live in studio is Victor Vitale. We also smoke blind taste test cigars 9 v 10, and 11 v 12. 
All this and the usual Cigar Authority shenanigans!
